<title type="html"><![CDATA[03/09 (Thu) How to argue better / Your thought and emotion affect your health (Host: Lawrence)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=707&amp;p=735#p735"><![CDATA[
03/09 (Thu) How to argue better / Your thought and emotion affect your health (Host: Lawrence)<br /><br />We will hold an on-site meeting only.<br />摩斯漢堡明曜店(每人低消 :60元)<br />台北市仁愛路4段151巷37號地下室.<br />MRT忠孝敦化站3號出口 , 明曜百貨後方第二個巷子口<br /><br />Royal 台北 ( Thursday )<br /><br />Meeting time agenda:7:00-9:00 PM<br />7:00-7:30  Chatting time with your favorite drink, and introduction of the meeting by the host<br />7:30-8:00  discussion of the first topic<br />8:00-8:05  Take a group photo<br />8:05-8:30  discussion of the second topic<br />8:30-9:00  table topic session (Whenever a question asked, the speaker is given 2 minutes for the impromptu presentation. Each table can use a cell phone as the timer.)<br /><br /><br />Session 1, how to argue better<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.everydayhealth.com/emotional-health/how-to-have-healthier-arguments-according-to-psychologists/">https://www.everydayhealth.com/emotiona ... hologists/</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1, Do you think argument is ok? Healthy or not?<br />2, Why did you have argument in your life, with whom? Why?<br />3, Share your recent personal experience?<br />4, In your opinion, how can we argue in healthy way?<br /><br /><br />--------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />Session 2 your thought and emotion affects your health<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.takingcharge.csh.umn.edu/how-do-thoughts-and-emotions-affect-health">https://www.takingcharge.csh.umn.edu/ho ... ect-health</a><!-- m --><br />1, What do you think of this article? What do you learn?<br />2, What do you think of your personality? Positive and cheerful or opposite? Why or why not?<br />3, Share your personal experience. In what way do you need to change your thought or emotion? How?<br />4, Do you have any story to share ----- thought and emotion affecting a person’s health?<br /><br /><br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=55735">zoe</a> — Fri Mar 03, 2023 7:56 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
